{"tid":2031021,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"雷鼎鳴指佔中令股市跌745點，每人損失5萬，咁國安法又令港人損失幾多？","createTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T11:12:52.000Z","uid":44930,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"874ebda8e04dcfd7f6097bff1a623269fa421deb","tid":2031021,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"科技大學經濟系教授雷鼎鳴昨在《晴報》撰文指<br />\n「佔領中環」行動發生以來，股市共跌745點<br />\n保守估計已造成股市等的經濟損失達到3,500億港元<br />\n相等於平均每名港人承受5萬元的損失，這還未計算影響未來發展的潛在損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2014/10/04/FI1410040006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2014%2F10%2F04%2FFI1410040006.htm&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=a78250b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2014/10/04/FI1410040006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n咁如今2020年5月22日，國安法消息一推出，港股就跌左1349點，跌幅逾5%<br />\n雷大師又認為港人又損失左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f70c67572258a7424d7cdbbb960952fc83e6f95","tid":2031021,"uid":76591,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"我睇你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1073d16745a01f7f254175bf8b99825ba59d634e","tid":2031021,"uid":81500,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"佔中大升市喎"},{"pid":"d9e4ad161c316739d33f70bd7c22e3017e47d92c","tid":2031021,"uid":9327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4fd30fe2a